{"tid":2229342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控訴當局迫害 俄異見女記者自焚亡","createTime":"2020-10-04T10:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T12:08:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d230086f28d197ac81910d22ac9b19a950c8af","tid":2229342,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201004/OCPDIZDWWJDKHON7MKMHOQ6GCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201004%2FOCPDIZDWWJDKHON7MKMHOQ6GCU%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=d2c17786\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201004%2FOCPDIZDWWJDKHON7MKMHOQ6GCU%2F&h=c5723c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201004/OCPDIZDWWJDKHON7MKMHOQ6GCU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n控訴當局迫害 俄異見女記者自焚亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yWR7psBU1jCnrBrreTx2mrPwofE=/1288x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UQ2NZILCY5EJ7HM2OK34MTMCDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyWR7psBU1jCnrBrreTx2mrPwofE%3D%2F1288x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUQ2NZILCY5EJ7HM2OK34MTMCDI.jpg&h=877d5850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■影片顯示斯萊文納在長椅上自焚。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯獨立新聞網Koza.Press總編輯斯萊文納（Irina Slavina）前日在下諾夫哥羅德市的內政部辦公室外自焚身亡，此前警方曾針對一個反對派組織到她家中突擊搜查。她死前數小時在社交網撰文說：「請把我的死歸咎於俄羅斯。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KEPZfaMl0SWBikcuoJmbS_R_aQs=/1573x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GFKHWFICF5FJXKRYENOI6DDCYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKEPZfaMl0SWBikcuoJmbS_R_aQs%3D%2F1573x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGFKHWFICF5FJXKRYENOI6DDCYE.jpg&h=7791dc97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民眾擺放蠟燭悼念。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾刊登反普京報道<br />\n<br />\n她上周四在社交網表示，軍警清晨突擊搜查她的住所，尋找反對派運動「開放俄羅斯」的文宣。該組織由異見者霍多爾科夫斯基資助，被指資助該市示威。搜查期間她向警方表示自己「甚麼都沒有」，惟警方照充公她一家三口的電腦和手機，「我沒辦法工作」。<br />\n<br />\n社交網流傳影片顯示她在一張長椅上自焚，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n社運人士奇科夫表示，萊文納曾被控不尊重政府和發放假新聞。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n調查委員會其後發聲明證實消息，指她的遺體「有燒傷的痕迹」，卻指「沒有基礎」把她的死與警方調查掛鈎，指她在調查中只屬證人，既非疑犯也非被告。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社/英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"bfae5c381a25682bca1e3126e62c878f39276a20","tid":2229342,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"香港國安法都遲早拘捕創作文宣既人"},{"pid":"a567c8b17951bf3e644258f5120739aec1c323b8","tid":2229342,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb139fe3ad5bdd762884e7ebd808cbc6e01366b","tid":2229342,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"⋯警方照充公她一家三口的電腦和手機⋯<br />\n香港成日發生啦！充公電腦手機，迫解鎖"},{"pid":"28e82583dd5c93736d38430ee284ac222354e560","tid":2229342,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfae5c381a25682bca1e3126e62c878f39276a20","tid":2229342,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"香港國安法都遲早拘捕創作文宣既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:08:31.000Z","msg":"發明文字既人都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}